## Scoring

**Likelihood:** 1 (very unlikely) → 5 (very likely)
**Impact:** 1 (minor inconvenience) → 5 (project-threatening)
**Priority = Likelihood × Impact** (1–25)

| Score | Action |
|---|---|
| 20–25 | Mitigate now — this is critical |
| 12–19 | Plan mitigation this sprint |
| 6–11 | Monitor; add to next sprint if score rises |
| 1–5 | Accept; log and revisit quarterly |

