## Risk categories

- **Requirements** — unclear scope, changing requirements, missing acceptance criteria
- **Technical** — complexity underestimated, design flaw, unknown integration, performance
- **Quality** — insufficient testing, test debt, QA skipped
- **Security** — data exposure, broken auth, dependency vulnerability, secrets leak
- **Operations** — deployment failure, no monitoring, no rollback, infra drift
- **Team** — knowledge silo, key person absent, blocked dependency, scope creep
- **Compliance** — {{COMPLIANCE}} requirements not met

