## Review cadence

- **Sprint planning:** review all open risks; close any resolved; add new ones from pre-mortem
- **Weekly:** check scores of risks rated 12+ — are they getting worse?
- **Post-incident:** add any risks that materialised as incidents so the pattern is documented
